section: The effects of natural disasters and suicidality
text:
The effects of natural disasters and suicidality






DESCRIBE

title: Catalina CaÃ±izares
text:
My passion lies in data science and its application to mental health-related issues. Recently, I have broadened my skill set by working extensively in both R and Python environments. My focus primarily lies in cleaning, understanding, and merging datasets, and conducting comprehensive data exploration analysis using an array of packages such as dplyr, ggplot2, purr, stringr, table1, gtsummary, skimr, and stats.
Lastly, I strongly believe in the principles of reproducible research, and I advocate for it by using Quarto and RMarkdown.
